		<p class="intropara">The purpose of the Inventory Project is to provide a framework and tools for displaying and analyzing landslide inventory data collected in a spatially aware digital format from individual states. However, there is a wealth of landslide inventory information that is not digital in nature, in the form of hard-copy reports, maps, and other formats, which will need to be scanned or otherwise integrated into a digital format. Most state surveys and the USGS  have information of a non-digital nature, and one of the challenges of the project is to successfully provide a forum for this valuable information.</p>
